  "title": "Part Time Teacher (Chemistry, Physics, Biology) | Various location",
  "description": "<p><strong>SECONDARY SCHOOL TEACHERS NEEDED:</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>***FULL & PART TIME***</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Secondary:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Physics</strong></li><li><strong>Chemistry</strong></li><li><strong>Biology</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Part Time: $33-45 per hour (commensurate with experience)</strong></p><p><strong>Full Time: $2200-3500 per month (commensurate with experience)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Working hours: </strong></p><p><strong>Full Time: Mon to Fri (8.30am to 5.30pm)</strong></p><p><strong>Part Time: between 9am to 4.30pm</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Locations: Various location</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />• Prepare and conduct lessons according to the course syllabus and scheme of work<br />• Provide necessary supervision to the students and report students’ discipline issues to the Student Affairs staff<br />• Schedule and prepare examination papers and assignments<br />• Monitor the performance and progress of each student, including academic counselling<br />• Give feedback to Management about the continual improvement of the class performance<br />• Mark and grade all course work, assignments and examination papers<br />• Give feedback to Management on the course proceedings at the end of semester/course/modules<br />• Participate in programme review meetings</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />• Minimum a Bachelors Degree<br />• At least 1 year of relevant experience</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p><strong>Please send in your resume to: recruit@dismanpower.com.sg & indicate in the subject as \"Secondary Teacher (indicate subject, Full/Part Time)\".</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>DIS Manpower Pte Ltd<br />EA License No.: 08C3226<br />EA Personnel: Sng Wei Lin<br />EA Reg No.: R1101806</p>",
